{"tid":1533611,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【置頂】不要再說警察還眼，試著說社會垃圾","createTime":"2019-09-02T18:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:48:49.000Z","uid":214984,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"96d7b1b949b99c9364b083ca9bc6318b9517e406","tid":1533611,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:22:09.000Z","msg":"由爆眼嗰日開始，狗內部全部都好支持射爆眼嗰個同伴。<br />\n<br />\n「還眼」呢個字係一開始要強調射眼呢個行為有幾可恥，但同狗對峙緊嘅時候，<span style=\"color: red;\">再叫「還眼」只會提醒佢哋爆眼嗰隻狗有幾咁受歡迎</span>。啲狗聽倒還眼，瞄天都即刻瞄翻隻眼（發唔發現自從爆眼之後啲狗多咗、合理化咗瞄頭）<br />\n<br />\n極多狗都有一種自我欺騙，<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得自己維護緊社會安定、喺萬人反對下做緊正確嘅事</span>。我哋嘅口號一定要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">提醒佢哋係社會嘅敗類</span></span>，係唔會有人支持嘅最低下階層，徹底打擊佢哋自以爲為緊社會付出嘅幻想。<br />\n<br />\n叫法可以喺「香港警察，社會垃圾」、街坊可以叫「xxx唔歡迎你哋」，「黑社會」相對上力度無咁強但都真係好過「還眼」<br />\n<br />\n老豆搵仔都出咗條好主意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7xRTHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7xRTHH.png&h=5dfbea42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察 過街曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b72ea11ef3c3bb9a813ff473974dcc7cc17a113b","tid":1533611,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a70bdb6049b9345342af6222b7c8801f08b8f6d","tid":1533611,"uid":249260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:23:47.000Z","msg":"香港警察 <br />\n社會敗類<br />\n禽獸不如"},{"pid":"3459bd3dd8e9834cee2b01a91c7bf754128d100e","tid":1533611,"uid":214984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:24:28.000Z","msg":"香港警察 人渣垃圾"},{"pid":"df53ec793cf06d865209444ff7e93d0269f19dbe","tid":1533611,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:24:45.000Z","msg":"強姦犯"},{"pid":"3203b3f3a997e9caddee3866124924f7598dd7a5","tid":1533611,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dis